Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.22,0:01:10.81,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I'm confident we can change the past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:15.99,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Hope to be with you even after rebirth.....Rebirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.14,0:01:23.13,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}今日が過去に変わる事で、明日が近づいて。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.38,0:01:30.38,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}そんな当たり前の事に　心は傷ついて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:34.46,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}あの日見た『世界』を　もう一度作ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.80,0:01:39.95,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}叶う時が　いつか来るなら　もう何もいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:47.74,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}まるで可能性が無いと　誰に揶揄されても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.12,0:01:52.60,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}次の君に逢える日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.79,0:01:56.55,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}繰り返し　巡る運命が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.81,0:01:59.91,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}たとえ　どんな道でも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:03.54,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}決して　決して　諦めない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:07.31,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}『あした、またね。』　その『未来』を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.49,0:02:11.10,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}いつまでも失くさないように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.53,0:02:14.65,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}終わりのない始まり
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:20.03,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}今、君と夢見たいから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.29,0:02:24.78,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}繋いだ手を　離さないでね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.78,0:02:27.96,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I'm confident we can change the past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.15,0:02:31.63,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Hope to be with you even after rebirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:33.84,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I'm confident we can change.
